text: Diede de Groot was the defending champion and successfully defended her Wheelchair Women's Singles tennis title at the 2019 US Open, defeating Yui Kamiji in the final, 4–6, 6–1, 6–4. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ===Finals=== == External links == * Draw Wheelchair Women's Singles U.S. Open, 2019 Women's Singles
